P(D|Y) 
P(D) = 0.001
P(Y|D) = 0.98   
P(Y|D^c) = 0.06   
P(D|Y) = \frac{P(Y|D)P(D)}{P(Y)}
D
D^c
P(Y) = P(Y \cap(D\cup D^c)) = P(Y\cap D) + P(Y\cap D^c) = P(Y|D)P(D) + P(Y|D^c)P(D^c) 
P(Y) = 0.98 \times 0.001 + 0.06 \times 0.999 = 0.06092
P(Y|D) = \frac{0.98 \times 0.001}{0.06092} = 0.016
